OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1777313467
OL,3,CTriple amputee war veteran completes
OL,4,CLondon Marathon
OL,6,FA triple amputee war veteran from St
OL,7,FHelens has successfully completed the
OL,8,FLondon Marathon.
OL,10,FAndy Reid MBE, who lost both legs and
OL,11,Fhis right arm in Afghanistan in 2009,
OL,12,Fcompleted the race in 12 and a half
OL,13,Fhours, quicker than his expected time
OL,14,Fof 13 hours.
OL,16,FHe braved the difficult conditions,
OL,17,Feven having to take his leg off at
OL,18,Fregular intervals during the 26.2 mile
OL,19,Fcourse.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1777313467
OL,3,CTriple amputee war veteran completes
OL,4,CLondon Marathon
OL,6,FAndy did the race to raise money to
OL,7,Fsupport other veterans, which pushed
OL,8,Fhim to make it to the finish line.
OL,10,FSpeaking to ITV's This Morning, he
OL,11,Fsaid: "I started training on 1
OL,12,FJanuary, I went out and did an eight
OL,13,Fmile walk.
OL,15,F"I've been training since then really.
OL,16,FWith prosthetics on it's obviously a
OL,17,Fbit harder work.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1777313467
OL,3,CTriple amputee war veteran completes
OL,4,CLondon Marathon
OL,6,F"I was sweating. I've got (fewer)
OL,7,Fextremities than normal people, but
OL,8,Fthe same blood in my body, so it's
OL,9,Fhard to cool down as well.
OL,11,F"So about every 2 miles I take a leg
OL,12,Foff, give it a wipe, give it a clean,
OL,13,Fput it back on again, and then go
OL,14,Fagain.
OL,16,F"Luckily I had a friend of mine, Ged
OL,17,FMason (OBE), carrying a chair for me,
OL,18,Fso we'd stop, pop the chair out, do
OL,19,Fwhat I needed to do, then we'd crack
OL,20,Fon again. So it was fantastic.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1777313467
OL,3,CTriple amputee war veteran completes
OL,4,CLondon Marathon
OL,6,FAndy is the first triple amputee to
OL,7,Fcomplete the London Marathon.
OL,9,FThe former corporal lost both his legs
OL,10,Fand an arm after stepping on a Taliban
OL,11,Fimprovised bomb while out on patrol in
OL,12,FAfghanistan.
OL,14,FThe 49-year-old completed the route in
OL,15,Fhonour of the seven members of his
OL,16,Fregiment, his friends, whom he lost,
OL,17,Fsaying: "I'm still here despite my
OL,18,Finjury, so I've got to make the most
OL,19,Fof life."
OL,26,@yD@IOU{D@IO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1777313467
OL,3,CTriple amputee war veteran completes
OL,4,CLondon Marathon
OL,6,FAndy has raised hundreds of thousands
OL,7,Fof pounds for various charities who
OL,8,Fhelped him over the years, including
OL,9,Fby abseiling down Blackpool tower and
OL,10,Fdoing a 600-mile tricycle ride.
OL,12,F"I was happy with (my time). I was
OL,13,Fanticipating 13 (hours) and I knew the
OL,14,Fcut-off point was 23:59, so yeah it
OL,15,Fwas a bit emotional at times, but I
OL,16,Fknow why I'm doing it, don't I?
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1777313467
OL,3,CTriple amputee war veteran completes
OL,4,CLondon Marathon
OL,6,F"It's to raise money to support other
OL,7,Fveterans with disabilities and also
OL,8,Fveterans with mental health and drug
OL,9,Fand alcohol issues as well, so that's
OL,10,Fin your mind when you're doing these
OL,11,Fthings.
OL,13,F"When it gets tough, you remember why
OL,14,Fyou're doing these kind of things, and
OL,15,Fyou dig in and you get to the end."
OL,17,FAndy was cheered on by the thousands
OL,18,Fwho gathered to support the
OL,19,Fparticipants at this year's race.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1777313467
OL,3,CTriple amputee war veteran completes
OL,4,CLondon Marathon
OL,6,FHe said: "The crowds were amazing,
OL,7,Flittle kids out there giving you a
OL,8,Fhigh five as you walked past and
OL,9,Fgiving you sweets and things like
OL,10,Fthat."
OL,12,FAndy's daughter Scarlett is hoping to
OL,13,Fshow off his medal at school.
OL,15,FHe added: "We'll get back up north
OL,16,Fthis afternoon and do the school run
OL,17,Ftomorrow, and she can take it in to
OL,18,Fshow and tell."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1777313467
OL,3,CTriple amputee war veteran completes
OL,4,CLondon Marathon
OL,6,FHe is raising money for the Army
OL,7,FBenevolent Fund (ABF) who helped him
OL,8,Fafter his injury, and for his own
OL,9,Fcharity the Standing Tall Foundation,
OL,10,Fwhich provides mental health
OL,11,Fcounselling, addiction, housing and
OL,12,Fwelfare support to veterans and
OL,13,Fcommunities in his home town.
OL,15,FWant more on the issues affecting the
OL,16,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,17,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,18,Four region.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/8
